1138.name: CuSiMn Tig
1138.Applications: Welding CuMn, CuSiMn, pure copper and copper alloys.
1138.Suitable_For: Welding thin steel plates and or galvanized plates in the car industry and also for cladding CuMn, CuSiMn and CuZn alloys. Suitable for cladding cast iron and un- and low alloyed steels.
